<li id="cite_note-Harris2015-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHarrisBringhurst2015" class="citation book cs1">Harris, Matthew L.; Bringhurst, Newell G. (2015). <span class="id-lock-limited" title="Free access subject to limited trial, subscription normally required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=Pn20CgAAQBAJ"><i>The Mormon Church and Blacks: A Documentary History</i></a></span>. Chicago: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-252-08121-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-252-08121-7"><bdi>978-0-252-08121-7</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mormon+Church+and+Blacks%3A+A+Documentary+History&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Illinois+Press&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-252-08121-7&amp;rft.aulast=Harris&amp;rft.aufirst=Matthew+L.&amp;rft.au=Bringhurst%2C+Newell+G.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DPn20CgAAQBAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoseph+Smith%27s+views+on+Black+people" class="Z3988"></span></span>
