<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Bible_(King_James)/Genesis#9:20" class="extiw" title="s:Bible (King James)/Genesis">Genesis 9:20–27</a></span>
